sequenceDiagram
    actor Admin
    participant AdminDashboard as Admin Dashboard
    participant QuestionBankController as Question Bank Controller
    participant Database

    Note over Admin,Database: UC-05: Manage Question Bank (CRUD)

    Admin->>AdminDashboard: Navigates to "Add New Question"
    AdminDashboard->>QuestionBankController: getTopics()
    QuestionBankController->>Database: fetchTopics()
    Database-->>QuestionBankController: list of topics
    QuestionBankController-->>AdminDashboard: return topics for dropdown
    AdminDashboard-->>Admin: Display input fields (LaTeX, Tiers, Topics)

    Admin->>AdminDashboard: Enters details & clicks "Save"
    AdminDashboard->>QuestionBankController: createQuestion(text, solution, topicId, tier)
    QuestionBankController->>QuestionBankController: validateInputFormat(LaTeX, required_fields)

    alt Invalid Input
        QuestionBankController-->>AdminDashboard: Error: "Missing fields or invalid math syntax"
        AdminDashboard-->>Admin: Show error & highlight fields
    else Input Valid
        par Persistence & Logic
            QuestionBankController->>Database: add_question(data)
            QuestionBankController->>Database: incrementTopicQuestionCount(topicId)
        end
        Database-->>QuestionBankController: success
        QuestionBankController-->>AdminDashboard: return success message
        
        AdminDashboard->>QuestionBankController: getUpdatedQuestionList()
        QuestionBankController->>Database: fetchQuestions()
        Database-->>QuestionBankController: questions_data
        QuestionBankController-->>AdminDashboard: Display Question Bank Dashboard (List View)
    end

    Note over Admin,Database: Phase 2: Management Flow (Decision Point)

    alt Admin chooses to Edit
        Admin->>AdminDashboard: Selects "Edit" on question
        AdminDashboard->>QuestionBankController: getQuestionDetails(id)
        QuestionBankController->>Database: fetchQuestionById(id)
        Database-->>QuestionBankController: question_object
        QuestionBankController-->>AdminDashboard: Fill form with current data
        Admin->>AdminDashboard: Modifies fields & clicks "Update"
        AdminDashboard->>QuestionBankController: updateQuestion(id, data)
        QuestionBankController->>Database: update_content(text, choices)
        Database-->>QuestionBankController: success
        QuestionBankController-->>AdminDashboard: Update confirmed
    else Admin chooses to Delete
        Admin->>AdminDashboard: Clicks "Delete" icon
        AdminDashboard-->>Admin: Prompt: "Confirm Soft Delete?"
        Admin->>AdminDashboard: Confirm
        AdminDashboard->>QuestionBankController: removeQuestion(id)
        QuestionBankController->>Database: update(is_active=False)
        Database-->>QuestionBankController: success
        QuestionBankController-->>AdminDashboard: Remove from active dashboard view
    end